# Venator UI monorepo

This is the Venator UI monorepo. When suggesting code:

- Use @venator-ui/ui for all UI primitives (Button, Card, Input, Modal, Table, Toast, Badge, etc.)
- Use @venator-ui/patterns for layouts (DashboardLayout, SidebarNav, Topbar, PageHeader, ModuleGrid, StatCard)
- Never use raw HTML elements when a Venator component exists
- Never use raw Tailwind classes for layout — use pattern components instead
- Dark mode is always supported via Tailwind darkMode: 'class'
- All components accept className prop for additional Tailwind classes
- CLI: npx @venator-ui/cli init <archetype> to scaffold architectures
- CLI: npx @venator-ui/cli add <pattern> to add individual patterns

## Package structure

- packages/ui — UI primitives source
- packages/patterns — layout patterns source
- packages/archetypes — archetype templates
- packages/tokens — design tokens and Tailwind preset
- packages/cli — CLI source
- apps/docs — Next.js documentation site

## Commands

- npm run build:packages — build all packages
- npm run dev — start docs dev server
